<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When Zend_Form_Decorator_ViewScript renders the view, it uses Zend_View_Helper_Partial, which supports two parameter formats.</p>

<p>The one that is supported is:
$view-&gt;partial($name, $model)</p>

<p>The one that is NOT supported is:
$view-&gt;partial($name, $module, $model)</p>

<p>Without this functionality, it is impossible to render a view script from a module other than current module.</p>

<p>Will submit a BC patch soon.</p>

    </div>
